window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Welcome back to Bryce, Colorado, a small town in the Rocky Mountains. Maggie's a divorced mom with two teenage sons. Owen is a retired US Marine who suffers from PTSD. When Maggie's best friend goes missing while on a mountain hike, Owen is called in to join the search and rescue team. Maggie joins too, as she knows the area where her friend disappeared better than anyone.</p> <p>Caught up in a sudden blizzard and facing dangerous conditions, Maggie needs Owen just as much as he needs her. This romantic suspense novel is filled with heart and feels, hurt and comfort, second chances, and lots more.<i> Lost and Found</i> is book two of the McIntyre Search and Rescue series.</p>"; 
